__SqlaTable__.sql:
SELECT 1.0 * COUNT(response_message) filter (WHERE response_message='No alert' and __time > MILLIS_TO_TIMESTAMP(TIMESTAMP_TO_MILLIS(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)-604800000))/
       COUNT(type) filter (WHERE type='Entry' and response_message='Not clean' and __time > MILLIS_TO_TIMESTAMP(TIMESTAMP_TO_MILLIS(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)-604800000)) as Compliance_Rate
FROM hospital
